      "description": "Kubota Pharmaceutical Holdings Co., Ltd. engages in the pharmaceutical and medical device business worldwide. The company offers eyeMO, a remote retinal monitoring device for home-based and patient self-monitoring optical coherence tomography; and a NASA high-res version OCT device. It also provides Emixustat HCI compounds for Stargardt disease indications in Phase 3 clinical trials, as well as pr",
